data.description: Nestled on an expansive half-acre lot, this exquisite 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and farmhouse charm. Step inside to discover durable wood-look tile floors, contemporary fixtures, and abundance of natural light that bathes the open-concept living area, complete with elegant white brick fireplace & shiplap accent wall. The kitchen features a large island, stainless farmhouse sink, pendant lighting, and cooktop. The spacious master suite pampers with walk-in tile shower, relaxing soaking tub, separate sinks, and deep walk-in closet. Laundry is no chore with the oversized utility room! 4th bedroom is currently used as an office configuration. Outside, escape into the countryside, complete with a generous covered patio overlooking the peaceful wildlife. The septic system was intentionally placed to allow for a future shop or pool! Experience true country living at its finest, all while enjoying the convenience of nearby amenities in Justin.
